subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Ana Ivanovic lost and Venus and Serena Williams advanced to the third round of the Italian Open in Rome. Ivanovic was upset by the qualifier Tsvetana Pironkova, 6-4, 5-7, 6-2. Venus Williams advanced to the third round by defeating Samantha Stosur, 6-4, 6-1; and Serena Williams routed Alona Bondarenko, 6-2, 6-0.
